  | Organize your inventory at multiple locations, including transfer routes. | [Set Up Locations](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dynamics365/business-central/inventory-how-register-new-items) |
  | Create item cards for inventory, noninventory, or service items that you trade in. | [Register New Items](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dynamics365/business-central/inventory-how-register-new-items) |
  | Use the **Copy Item** function to quickly create a new item card based on an existing one. | [Copy Existing Items to Create New Items](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dynamics365/business-central/inventory-how-copy-items) |
